•
This weekend the Shop employees challenged the Innetech crew to a special Game of Skate tournament in the Pro Course.
—
The rules were simple; 
• 2 skaters from each crew 
• 3 games of skate 
 - One game on Flat
 - Two games on Pro Course obstacles 
—
With bragging rights (and lunch) on the line the two squads battled it out for SPoT supremacy...who did you have ur money on??!
—
Teams
Innetech: @rolo.c & @marsefarmer_ 
Shop Guys: @timgasiorski & @skatestoppers_ 
—
📱: @bowser_media_lab 
#SPoTSkateBattle #SPoTTeam #SPoTTampa

@louielopez x @volcomskate collection is here. ⚫️⚪️

Louie is featured in his new Tapered Corduroy Pants. Volcom worked closely with Louie to create a signature collection, and these cords epitomize Louie’s passion for both skateboarding and easy streetwear style. 100% cotton corduroy is tailored to be loose in the thighs for maximum movement, tapering to a 17” leg opening that skates well and looks sharp.

Available now on SPoTTampa.com 🔥

#volcom #louielopez #SPoTTampa
